1. etherium has two types of accounts user accounts and contract accounts.
contract account is hte address where the contract is deployed and when a message is sent to this 
address the contract code gets executed

2. Ehtereum does not sue APplicaiton specific integreated circuit ( ASIC ) for mining rather it uses memory intestive computations for mining problems.
3. MAIDSAFE AND NXT are teh alternates to ethereum technology
